 :drone: n. Ignorant sales or customer service personnel in computer or
electronics superstores. Characterized by a lack of even superficial
knowledge about the products they sell, yet possessed of the conviction that
they are more competent than their hacker customers. Usage: "That video board
probably sucks, it was recommended by a drone at Fry's" In the year 2000,
their natural habitats include Fry's Electronics, Best Buy, and CompUSA.